id":"27382dea28c60f6ffd7893846428a5957d659c47","tid":180030,"uid":29059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:23:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>fish 靚仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁同普通人比係唔差嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我意思係會因為佢外型而大家覺得佢可憐多dd<br />\n平時身邊嘅人係咁嘅 你當佢係痴線佬就完咗啦"},{"pid":"447ccacfbffd95eaae90dca6f2526d55e3f98ed7","tid":180030,"uid":90839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:07:57.000Z","msg":"留明等睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05c7b0e697de619cc410ba4d9e2aa451a6b26ca","tid":180030,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T11:55:06.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇完 好心嗡<br />\nFisher發現志偉收埋鎚仔個幕明明係好悲哀好貼地嘅一幕<br />\n但全院嘅人睇見之後係笑<br />\n啊伯個一輪粗口屌尻fisher痴線佬入返青山<br />\n全院人係大笑<br />\n睇完有種無力感湧出黎<br />\n<br />\n好鍾意credit前個句說話<br />\n意思大概係叫人用心去了解身邊事物，用眼係唔能夠睇到事實嘅全部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黃進 好有驚喜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60cc72d5099203d2b87680df74d243d8355fb0f","tid":180030,"uid":9281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:04:49.000Z","msg":"睇金燕𤤗 做呢啲角色睇到好厭"},{"pid":"e627b1d78e2519096956116073dda11fb77a37c9","tid":180030,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:07:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇金燕𤤗 做呢啲角色睇到好厭</blockquote><br />\n戲骨嘛"},{"pid":"8113f2855ed9e27984abe5b9fb56e6668dde17a1","tid":180030,"uid":82310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:00:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱睇完 好心嗡<br />\nFisher發現志偉收埋鎚仔個幕明明係好悲哀好貼地嘅一幕<br />\n但全院嘅人睇見之後係笑<br />\n啊伯個一輪粗口屌尻fisher痴線佬入返青山<br />\n全院人係大笑<br />\n睇完有種無力感湧出黎<br />\n<br />\n好鍾意credit前個句說話<br />\n意思大概係叫人<strong>用心去了解身邊事物，用眼係唔能夠睇到</strong>事實嘅全部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黃進 好有驚喜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n「再見了。」小王子說。<br />\n「再見。對了，我要告訴你一個祕密，很簡單的秘密。<br />\n<strong>就是用心才能看見真實。<br />\n真正重要的事，用眼睛是看不見的。」</strong><br />\n小王子跟著複誦了一遍，以便牢記在心裡。"}]}